  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You aim your blow to break a bone, to maim your foe and hobble them in this fight. Make a melee Taijutsu attack at disadvantage as you aim your blow at a specific location. On a hit, you deal your [weapons damage] and choose a which bone you broke below:</p><p>Shoulder: The target creature has disadvantage on Melee attacks until they are either healed with a Medical jutsu cast at B-Rank or higher or spend a Full Turn Action setting it back into place.</p><p>Shin: Target creature takes 1d6 force damage for every 5 feet they willingly move. They also have disadvantage on Saving Throws that would forcibly move them</p>",
